DCSh2T</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[PR0CR45T184T0R]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Elongate</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/UtAsAxv</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/TkyxinU.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/UtAsAxv</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[fulcrims]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Got my name and gender changed today</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/DuU3bn9</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/37Go22e.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I wasn't sure if it was too late and I was so terrified, living in a red state (Utah), that I might get a judge who would deny me. Instead, I got one who was super nice, who went out of his way to congratulate and compliment a woman who was adopting her wife's biological child, and dealt with several trans people all getting our names and/or genders legally changed. 

The records are sealed and Utah currently allows you to change all of your documents. I am hoping to get them changed swiftly, so that all of my documents show my new name and gender, so no one will know otherwise unless we are naked together (and by that point I really hope they'd know!)

Anyway, I'm so excited I cried for a half hour afterward. I can't believe I'm really here. It feels so incredibly validating.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/DuU3bn9</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[PlanckEraWasMyBestEra]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Cat Dump-ilation:  Just cats, only cats, pure cat stuff</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/NhPRi1k</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/AqbImsu.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/I9ucnUA.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/7YDtJKb.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/53UKd0x.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ZGAJITg.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/uVQFt5Q.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/EIigGzR.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/TwjNMJ1.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/kaLr0pN.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/sqCk5YJ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/4nwx6MQ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/pBnTqqE.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/vp7ZqYb.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></di